%h2 Gas infrastructure
.help-block
  %p
    In the table below you can edit the specifics of the gas infrastructure of your LES.
    Three types of network components can be chosen:
    %ul
      %li
        %strong Pipes:
        depending on the pressure level differnt types of pipes can be chosen
      %li
        %strong Connectors:
        connect pressure levels and allow gas to move from high to low pressure
      %li
        %strong Compressors:
        connect pressure levels and allow gas to move from low to high pressure with loss
    More information about the gas network and its components can be found in the
    = succeed '.' do
      %a(href='https://github.com/quintel/etmoses/wiki/Gas-network') documentation

.empty-button{ class: ('hidden' if gas_asset_list.any?) }
  %button.btn.btn-primary Add new Gas Asset

%table.table.single.interactions.gas_assets{ data: { type: "gas_asset_list_table", url: get_types_testing_ground_gas_asset_lists_path(testing_ground) } }
  %thead
    %tr
      %th.col-sm-1{ data: { header: 'pressure_level_index' } } Pressure level
      %th{ data: { header: 'part' } } Asset
      %th{ data: { header: 'type' } } Type
      %th.col-sm-2{ data: { header: 'units' } } Quantity
      %th{ data: { header: 'stakeholder' } } Stakeholder
      %th.col-sm-1{ data: { header: 'building_year' } } Building year
      %th.col-sm-1{ data: { header: 'technical_lifetime' } } Technical lifetime
      %th.col-sm-1{ data: { header: 'initial_investment' } } Initial investment
      %th.col-sm-1{ data: { header: 'yearly_o_and_m_cost' } } Yearly O&M cost
      %th
      %th

  %tfoot.hidden
    = render partial: 'gas_asset_lists/table_row', locals: { list_item: InstalledGasAsset.new }

  %tbody
    - gas_asset_list.each do |list_item|
      = render partial: 'gas_asset_lists/table_row', locals: { list_item: list_item }
